Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.83,0:00:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都在期望著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.64,0:00:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期望有一天自己能夠成為特別的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.05,0:00:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期望有一天能夠找到會認可自己才能的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.57,0:00:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早在很久以前我就一直想像自己是一位守護在公主身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.62,0:00:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經歷了無數戰鬥的騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.24,0:00:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而  看來我錯過了那趟夢想的列車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.31,0:00:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.49,0:00:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏是我最喜歡的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.55,0:00:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜  沒有人流的車站
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.94,0:00:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很適合一個人看書
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.36,0:00:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  今天卻有一位客人捷足先登了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.92,0:01:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個車站是沒有電車的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.31,0:01:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.48,0:01:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.02,0:01:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我第一次和她相遇的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.11,0:01:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一次不足四十五秒的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.83,0:03:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  真搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不出去取材一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.60,0:03:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  是景啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.11,0:03:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.78,0:03:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥可別忘記參加晚會哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便去露個臉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  CUT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.64,0:03:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍到好畫面了嗎  京介
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.13,0:03:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只拍好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實下雪就最好不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.98,0:03:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行  拼接場景的時候就夠嗆的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:03:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過算了  反正也是取材
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃飯去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.69,0:04:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.93,0:04:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.75,0:04:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  只是覺得把宣傳海報拍下來也不錯的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是看到好女孩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然又來了  又來了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.85,0:04:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.95,0:04:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  歡迎回來  景學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  瑞希
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕店人太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.54,0:04:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  哥哥人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎  他到底還要不要來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.67,0:04:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都跟他說了這次再放鴿子就絕對不會放過他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:04:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紘學長好像總是那麼忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.05,0:04:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明沒有參加社團活動也沒有上補習班
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.00,0:05:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定有別的原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.05,0:05:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞希來幫我擺放一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.08,0:05:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.42,0:05:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真是個奇怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前我還以為他在想事情  結果突然發瘋似的撓頭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好像是在最後期限前趕工的漫畫家一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.89,0:05:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  景學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.54,0:05:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再發次短信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕快樂  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.75,0:05:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像來得有點晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來裏面是這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.27,0:06:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彌撒儀式已經結束了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我並不是教徒  只是想來取材
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.02,0:06:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.04,0:06:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一個非見不可的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.59,0:06:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在等人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.04,0:06:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  請留步
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.41,0:06:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.03,0:06:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慢  現在在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.92,0:06:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  景這傢伙生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小偷！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.27,0:06:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  那邊的人  你看見一輛摩托車嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.14,0:06:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.12,0:06:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道他往哪邊跑了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  這個借我下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.53,0:07:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的自行車
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這自行車小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼喂喂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  哥哥你該不會把晚會的事給忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒忘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.58,0:07:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是放鴿子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.22,0:07:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼突然改主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.99,0:07:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有去舞蹈會的禮服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是白雪公主嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.99,0:07:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我現在是灰姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.28,0:07:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不都一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.11,0:07:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在沒空和你扯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.95,0:07:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  難道突然接到工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.58,0:07:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  現在很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.24,0:07:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再聯絡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說下次再聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.11,0:07:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥那個笨蛋  去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死…死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.02,0:07:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的自行車
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.35,0:07:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.49,0:08:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,119嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救護車來之後  我還要陪她一起去醫院啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.40,0:08:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該還活著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.78,0:08:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  我怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.04,0:08:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼問我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.86,0:08:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.40,0:08:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不安分點躺著怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我東西被偷了  我最重要的挎包被偷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你撞到頭的話怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.54,0:08:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是等救護車來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  那挎包很貴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.50,0:08:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裏面還有錢包和手機
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.15,0:09:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要抓住那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.66,0:09:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.66,0:09:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜裏的公園還真能讓人平靜下來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.35,0:09:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個小偷怎麼了  不是說一定要把他抓到的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.42,0:09:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑得太久  累死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.26,0:09:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄得也太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算啦算啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.22,0:09:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正錢包裏面又沒有錢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.80,0:09:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電話裏面也只有奶奶家的電話而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.18,0:09:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個挎包也差不多想換了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.37,0:09:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和剛才說的差太遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.34,0:09:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.03,0:09:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼疼的地方  或者是想吐的感覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒有  完全沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.33,0:09:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許只是本人感覺不到而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟暈了過去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.37,0:09:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪有暈過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.71,0:09:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明一下子失去了意識
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:10:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人  完全沒有一點記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.71,0:10:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是  不可能有人在暈過去以後還知道自己在幹什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是那樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.45,0:10:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.62,0:10:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能為我擔心  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.49,0:10:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說  說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.15,0:10:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是溫柔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了  總之還是去一趟醫院比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我會考慮的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.97,0:10:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是雪  下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.53,0:10:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得這樣也很不錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.94,0:10:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和別人一起的白色耶誕節
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.60,0:10:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也  也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.20,0:10:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  太冷淡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的日子一個人過的話太孤單了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.57,0:11:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  我就算一個人也可以活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.59,0:11:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不大喜歡一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.94,0:11:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒告訴你我的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.43,0:11:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是宮村宮子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.38,0:11:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是廣野紘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廣野紘  是廣紘嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺奇怪的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.60,0:11:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮村宮子  宮宮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈  說起來還真是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.78,0:11:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你發現有趣的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.44,0:11:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦袋真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  廣野同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.48,0:11:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.18,0:11:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家裏今晚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.02,0:11:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都不在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.88,0:11:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才在想色色的事情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.59,0:11:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.84,0:11:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說嘛  家裏的鑰匙也都在那個挎包裏面了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.21,0:11:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣  就算回到家也進不了門
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:12:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚就要露宿街頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓一個女孩子在外面通宵的話不是很不安全嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.54,0:12:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說  要我陪你一起露宿街頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.65,0:12:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俗話說  一不做二不休
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.43,0:12:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.49,0:12:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}等一下  我才不要和你  我還有事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.29,0:12:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來今年的耶誕節要結束  還早得很
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.21,0:12:31.21,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現實
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.21,0:12:31.21,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}理想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在放學的班會上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發下來了志願調查
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同於小時候憧憬的未來的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.52,0:12:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是要具體地確定自己的將來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.46,0:12:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要成為在災難中為保護公主而戰的王子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不是可以寫那種夢想的歲數了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我錯過了那趟夢想的列車
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.66,0:13:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.87,0:13:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  為什麼要來問我？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.07,0:13:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想聽聽成年人的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.13,0:13:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得如果是火村先生的話  可能會給我什麼好建議吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.59,0:13:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾  我既不是牧師也不是心理諮詢師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  你一直待在這裏的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也難怪我要和你商量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是要在這裏等人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.15,0:13:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.13,0:13:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有喜歡的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.19,0:13:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的東西嗎？  讀書吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.34,0:13:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜歡讀小說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.62,0:13:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.43,0:13:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以去讀文科大學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.72,0:13:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後去做與出版社有關的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還可以自己寫小說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  把喜歡的事情變為職業
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.43,0:13:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是太武斷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.19,0:13:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總比把討厭的事情變為工作好上千倍了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:13:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要煩惱了  好好考慮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:13:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建議結束
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.87,0:14:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的成人的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.98,0:14:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成年人的…意見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得似懂非懂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正說到底  還是要自己考慮是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得那麼簡單…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.39,0:14:20.15,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.39,0:14:20.15,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}思念
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.09,0:14:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是妨礙到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.73,0:14:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.35,0:14:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我可以問你一個奇怪的問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.20,0:14:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前和我見過面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.91,0:14:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我們是見過面的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.35,0:14:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  其實也只是一面之緣而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.80,0:14:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.32,0:15:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你經常來這裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  只是偶爾來而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.07,0:15:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏很安靜  是個好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  這裏真是個得天獨厚的讀書的好地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  還能體驗Stand  by  Me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}注：出自1986年的一部美國電影
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.25,0:15:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.10,0:15:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在鐵路上走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為在這裏玩的話沒人會罵嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.58,0:15:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很有意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.70,0:15:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.84,0:15:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.97,0:15:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字是新藤千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.55,0:15:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獅子會把孩子推進千尋的山谷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫法就是這個千尋  讀作chihiro
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是麻生蓮治
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.27,0:15:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麻生同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.86,0:15:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.95,0:15:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋真早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.81,0:15:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  上次也是你比我先來到這裏的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有去學校上學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.75,0:16:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有去  學校嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.63,0:16:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.82,0:16:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.59,0:16:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.42,0:16:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.60,0:16:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏明明是麻生同學的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.72,0:16:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裏會給你添麻煩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得你好像有點平靜不下來的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.84,0:16:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.51,0:16:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不是那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.40,0:16:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也在考慮和你同樣的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是因為我在這裏  讓千尋不能安靜地讀書
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.77,0:16:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒有那麼想過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也別在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家在附近嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.35,0:16:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我還想在這裏待一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.34,0:16:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天已經黑了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.14,0:16:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想待在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.77,0:16:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.89,0:16:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.13,0:17:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  還能再到這裏來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.14,0:17:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.66,0:17:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.44,0:17:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  再見…啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.23,0:17:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  下次再見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:31.60,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:31.60,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}願望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.72,0:17:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.84,0:17:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼也沒有看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.40,0:17:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.68,0:17:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在看天空
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.23,0:17:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  是指什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,0:17:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  我只是覺得你和昨天有點不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.40,0:17:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  難道你是麻生同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.95,0:18:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我沒錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.88,0:18:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.00,0:18:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的「再見」…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.30,0:18:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「再見」是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.47,0:18:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你怎麼了  千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.96,0:18:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  不是那樣的  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  哎呀  我  為什麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.27,0:18:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你問我為什麼也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.35,0:18:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  我不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.17,0:18:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事  對不起  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.72,0:18:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問  為什麼今天麻生同學你會來到這裏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.21,0:18:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.91,0:18:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不知不覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:18:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.31,0:19:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.53,0:19:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太高興了  一下子誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.01,0:19:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  真的  請你忘掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.13,0:19:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  見到我她很高興嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.28,0:19:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  明明只見過三次面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.07,0:19:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不至於抱著我哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.45,0:19:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.74,0:19:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻生同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個口袋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這是我最近在讀的小說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.11,0:19:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡小說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.68,0:19:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就好像文字中毒一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.74,0:19:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口袋裏經常放了幾本
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒帶書的話  就好像重量少了  會感覺很不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.22,0:19:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像是貓的鬍子一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.55,0:19:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.26,0:19:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋的那本書
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.39,0:19:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是貓的鬍子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.09,0:19:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.86,0:19:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這個的話我就活不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你和我一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.72,0:19:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻生同學  我有一個請求  你能答應我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能和我  成為朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.69,0:20:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.22,0:20:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不願意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.24,0:20:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會  怎麼可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是  想讓你成為我的朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.41,0:20:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.90,0:20:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.22,0:20:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.36,0:20:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.64,0:20:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻生同學說完這句話以後回家去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.75,0:20:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.49,0:20:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻生同學和昨天的我約定好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.54,0:20:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來和今天的我見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.06,0:20:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的我  也和他約定好了明天再見面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.01,0:20:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  他還和這樣的我成為了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.38,0:21:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明想好了  不能為了這種事而放縱自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.17,0:21:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,景姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.23,0:23:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人再度相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.84,0:23:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷惘的時間又再一次開始轉動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.47,0:23:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  ef  -  a  tale  of  memories
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.11,0:23:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.02,0:23:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有不願忘卻的回憶嗎
